gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Rockets 135, Wizards 119
gameRecap.excerpt: Jalen Green records a season-high 37 points, along with eight rebounds and five 3PM to lead the Rockets over the Wizards, 135-119. Fred VanVleet (27 points, nine assists) and Amen Thompson (20 points, 10 rebounds, four assists, three steals) added 47 more in the victory, while Jordan Poole tallied 25 points and five 3PM for the Wizards in the losing effort. The Rockets improve to 31-35 on the season, while the Wizards fall to 11-55.
